channel.title: I'm pretty happy! My torrent was downloaded 7000 times!
channel.description:
Nobody cares ya ya blah blah, but since I don't really know what to do, I posted this.
It's been dowloaded 7000 times and I have seen ppl talking about it on forums I have never even been to. (I used google)
It's my ePSXe torrent download. It works for both Windows and Linux and has all the plugins. I didn't realize how popular it would become though. This was my first torrent I made. ;)
Torrent Details: Demonoid: http://www.demonoid.com/files/details/427655/ TorrentSpy: http://www.torrentspy.com/torrent/833235/PSX_Emulator_ePSXe_for_Windows_and_Linux_with_Plugins
My other torrent I made was downloaded only 500 times. [PSX] Lunar 2 Eternal Blue Disk 1, 2, and 3. (1.07 GB) Demonoid: http://www.demonoid.com/files/details/433328/9196808/ TorrentSpy: http://www.torrentspy.com/torrent/840092/PSX_Lunar_2_Eternal_Blue_Disk_1_2_and_3
All my torrents on demonoid. (6 of them are unseeded but thats cause Emuparadise's tracker is messed up. http://www.demonoid.com/files/?uid=1149601&seeded=2
~Ron
